TextEng: I want to ask you some questions.
Me want some informations.
Goodbye.
I hunt a cult that prolonged the Neverwinter plague.
Text: 저는 네버윈터 역병을 연장시킨 사교를 추적하고 있습니다.

TextEng: Tell me about your town.
Have you heard of any trouble around here?
Me looks for plague-cult. They hurt Neverwinter.
Text: 나 역병 사교 찾아. 걔들 네버윈터 해쳤어.

TextEng: You tells me abouts Charwood.
Maybe you hear about odd stuff or rumors?
I want to go over some things you said before.
Text: 전에 말씀하신 것들 다시 짚어보고 싶은데요.

TextEng: Me wants go over things you say before.
Text: 나 전에 말한 거 다시 물어봐.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Insight]</Start> Mayor, it's not morning. The darkness clings to this place.
Text: <StartCheck>[통찰]</Start> 시장님, 지금은 아침이 아닙니다. 어둠이 이곳에 드리워져 있어요.

TextEng: That isn't right. Do you even know the season?
Text: 그건 옳지 않습니다. 지금이 무슨 계절인지는 아시나요?

TextEng: Mayor, if there is a threat, perhaps I can help?
Text: 시장님, 위협이 있다면 제가 도와드릴 수 있을지도 모르겠네요.

TextEng: Jhareg? Who's that?
What stories?
You sound nervous. Are your lords fair?
You scared. They be fair guys?
<StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> Come now, there's no harm in talking to me.
Text: <StartCheck>[설득]</Start> 이봐요, 저한테 얘기해도 아무런 해가 없어요.

TextEng: <StartCheck>[Persuade]</Start> You tell me. There no problem with me.
Speak! Or you'll have more immediate things to fear!!
Text: 말하시오! 아니면 더 당장 두려워할 일이 생길 겁니다!!

TextEng: Me get mad if you not keep talking!
You can tell me. Can't you, handsome?
You tell me, good looking. Me your friend.
I will discover what happened to your children.
Text: 당신 아이들에게 무슨 일이 있었는지 알아내겠습니다.

TextEng: Me find out what happen to kids.
Text: 나 아이들 무슨 일 있었는지 찾아낼 거야.

TextEng: Is the castle dangerous? I will likely check it out.
Text: 성이 위험한가요? 아마 가서 확인해볼 것 같은데요.

TextEng: Me search castle probably. It safe?
Nothing to do with me. Goodbye.
Text: 제가 상관할 일이 아니네요. 안녕히 계세요.

TextEng: Nothing me care about. G'bye.
I want to ask some different questions.
Me ask different stuff.
Why don't you remember anything?
Text: 왜 아무것도 기억 못 하시는 거죠?

TextEng: Why you not remember stuff?
That not be right. You even know da season?
Text: 그거 이상해. 지금 무슨 계절인지 알아?

TextEng: If there be threat, maybe me can help?
Text: 위협 있으면 나 도와줄 수 있어?

TextEng: Jar-Egg? Who that be?
Uh, what stories?
